text:
Useless product from revolt. They claim range of the bike to be 150Kms on Eco Mode but in Real life it gives you about 70-80 Kms of Range in Eco Mode. I'm saying this because i'm using it from 4 months now. Seating is also very uncomfortable of this bike ( both of driver and the pillion) . All the features of this bike are a Hit and Miss , sometimes they work super fine and sometimes they don't work at all. And also I have to mention that the Keyless Feature of the bike is also not very long lasting as the Provided Keys have very short life and Once the Key's batteries are dead , you can't just get that batteries replaced either you have to replace the whole lock to get the new keys , and it will surely cost you way more than to just get the batteries of keys to be replaced.


Totally Unhappy with the ride quality also because tuning of Break and acceleration is soooo poor that Driving this bike in a City traffic is a Headache. A feather touch to a break gets Power to be cutted from the accelerator and as you remove the fingers from the brakes , all of sudden power is driven like a Spaceship which can cause a accident.


And at last , ofcourse the build quality of the bike is very cheap and pathetic. It doesn't even feel like that you're spending approx 2 lakhs to get this piece of shit.
